overview: Brighten up the holidays with the ORIGINAL World Famous JINGLE CATS "Real Kittens Sing Holiday Classics" now available on DVD. This fun, entertaining video features the nine original singing cats -- Cheesepuff, Max, Binky, Sprikenz, Petunia, Graymer, Clarisse, Cueball and Twizzler. Jingle Cats have more than 3.5 million hits on YouTube in clips from this DVD. It's a great gift for any cat person.
title: Jingle Cats Christmas
